title: (Weds Part 1) Amy Has Some “Alone Time” Planned for Her Birthday…Should We Be Worried? + Mike D did Something Weird During Weight Loss Journey

description:
Amy reveals that she is taking some ‘alone time’ to celebrate her birthday this weekend….we want to know if we need to be concerned with where she is going. Mike D reveals a weird thing he found that worked for him during his journey of losing 100 pounds.
